                                ʿEsavnyn</emph>; a scribal error. | TKow.01: <emph>ʿEsavɣa</emph>. |
                            H: <emph>ʿEsavɣa</emph>. | C: <emph>ʿEsavɣa</emph>.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Deut-002-fn2" type="footnote">Interlinear insertion by another
                            hand. | TKow.01: <emph>daɣyn</emph>. | H: <emph>daɣyn</emph>. | C:
                                <emph>daɣyn</emph>.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Deut-002-fn3" type="footnote">A mistranslation. | TKow.01:
                                <emph>Ḥacerimde</emph>; unvocalized text. | H:
