                                <emph>salalarda</emph>. | Heb. <foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">בַּחֲצֵרִים </foreign>
                             ‘in villages’.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Deut-002-fn4" type="footnote">K: <emph>qatyrdy</emph>; a
                            scribal error. | TKow.01: <emph>qattyrdy</emph>. | H:
                                <emph>qattyrdy</emph>. | C: <emph>qattyrdy</emph>.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Deut-002-fn5" type="footnote">TKow.01: <emph>bujurdu</emph>;
